  "reference_number": "RUS1978",
  "remarks": "\nWalter MORETTI is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 in that MORETTI is or has been involved in gaining a benefit from the Government of Russia through working as a director of companies carrying out business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian financial services sector and the Russian defence sector; and is or has been involved in making available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine \n",
